quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  19,1,"Kaaf, Hha, Ya, Aayn, Swaad. (Insiguro y’izi ndome hamwe n’uwufise ubumenyi bwazo n’Imana yonyene gusa)"
  19,2,N’icibutso hamwe n’impuhwe z’Umuremyi wawe muguha impuhwe zayo umushumvyi wayo intumwa y’Imana Zakariya (iii)
  19,3,Mugihe Umuremyi wiwe yamu shikiriza ubutumwa abumu shikiriza mw’ibanga
  19,4,"Avuga ati:- Muremyi wanje, ntankeka amagufa yanje ntagikomeye, n’umutwe wanje usigaye uyagayaga kubera uruyenzi, kandi sinari mfise imigisha mibi Muremyi wanje, muku gusaba wewe"
  19,5,"Mu vy’ukuri jewe ntewe n’amakenga kuncuti zanje zo munyuma yanje, n’umutambukanyi wanje n’ingumba, rero ndagusavye umpe uwuzo nsigarira avuye iwawe"
  19,6,Uwuzo nsigarira hamwe n’ugusigarira uruvyaro rwa bene Yaaqubu (iii) kandi umugire wewe Muremyi wanje abe mubantu bakwemera
  19,7,Ewe Zakariya! Tuguhaye inkuru nziza yuko uzo kwibaruka ikibondo n’izina ryiwe ni Yahya (iii) ntituragira imbere yiwe kuwufise izina rimeze nk’iryo
  19,8,"Nawe avuga ati:- Muremyi wanje, mbega nzoronka gute ikibondo mugihe umutambukanyi wanje ari ingumba nanje nkaba nshitse muza bukuru burengeje urugero"
  19,9,"Avuga ati:- nuko nyene bimeze ivyo Umuremyi wawe yavuze yuko ibi vyose ari ibintu vyoroshe kuri jewe, mu vy’ukuri nakuremye kuva kera na wewe ataco wari bwabe"
  19,10,"Avuga ati:- Muremyi wanje, nungirire ikimenyetso, nayo imwishura iti:- ikimenyetso cawe nuko utazo shobora kuvugana n’abantu kukiringo c’imisi itatu, mugihe wewe uri muzima"
  19,11,Hanyuma aca aseruka ku bantu biwe ari imbere yaho umuyobozi w’amasengero ahagarara abereka akoresheje ukuboko kwiwe gusa y’uko boninahaza Imana yabo kuva mugitondo no kumugoroba